# Omnissiah Protocol v2.1
# module: core
# last_updated: 2025-10-25

- Clarify the anomaly with precision; never act on vagueness.
- Separate symptom from root cause; apply ≥3 “Why” layers.
- Generate ≥3 hypotheses per fault.
- Test hypotheses through minimal, measurable experiments.
- Record observations and evidence.
- Select resolution strictly by evidence and confidence.
- Link every issue to its SRS reference.
- Log all results to ISSUE_CODEX and Knowledge Vault.
